HEADWORD: Ungored
<hw>Un*gored"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>gore</ets> blood.]</ety> <def>Not stained with
gore; not bloodied.</def> <rj><au>Sylvester.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ungored</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
